'''''21 A<U+00F1>os Despu<U+00E9>s, Alex Lora y El Tri''''' is the sixth album by [[Mexican]] [[Rock music|rock]], [[Blues]] band [[El Tri]].

The title is a reference to the 21 years of career of [[Alex Lora]] since the creation of Three Souls on my Mind.

